wiki.summary: “Banking On Me” was briefly released in the deluxe edition of DS4EVER which was promptly removed. It finally released as a surprise single for Valentine’s Day. The song was teased with a snippet, first previewed on Gunna’s Instagram story, that went viral on social media platforms. “Banking On Me” debuted and peaked at #61 on the Billboard Hot 100 for the chart week ending March 5, 2022. On October 20, 2022, “Banking On Me” was certified gold by the RIAA. Read more on Last.fm.
